OL,3,CPublic inquiry into Omagh bomb to
OL,4,Cbegin hearings
OL,6,FThe public inquiry into the Omagh
OL,7,Fbombing is to hold its first
OL,8,Fsubstantive hearings.
OL,10,FBereaved families and survivors are
OL,11,Fexpected to gather at the Strule Arts
OL,12,FCentre in the Co Tyrone town on
OL,13,FTuesday for the inquiry which will
OL,14,Fexamine whether the atrocity could
OL,15,Freasonably have been prevented by UK
OL,16,Fauthorities.
