OL,3,CPublic inquiry into Omagh bomb to
OL,4,Cbegin hearings
OL,6,FScottish judge Lord Turnbull is
OL,7,Foverseeing the probe into the 1998
OL,8,FReal IRA bombing which claimed 29
OL,9,Flives, including a woman pregnant with
OL,10,Ftwins.
OL,12,FCommemorative and personal statement
OL,13,Fhearings will be held over the next
OL,14,Ffour weeks.
OL,16,FThese will begin with bereaved
OL,17,Ffamilies giving pen portrait evidence
OL,18,Fof those who died, followed by
OL,19,Fsurvivors, emergency services and
OL,20,Fthose working in statutory
OL,21,Forganisations.
