OL,3,CPublic inquiry into Omagh bomb to
OL,4,Cbegin hearings
OL,6,FAccording to the inquiry schedule,
OL,7,FTuesday will hear commemorations of
OL,8,FFernando Blasco Baselga, 12, and Rocio
OL,9,FAbad Ramo, 23, two Spanish nationals
OL,10,Fkilled in the bombing.
OL,12,FThe proceedings were announced by then
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland secretary Chris
OL,14,FHeaton-Harris in 2023 after a High
OL,15,FCourt judgment recommended a public
OL,16,Finquiry into alleged security failings
OL,17,Fin the lead-up to the atrocity, and
OL,18,Falso urged the Irish authorities to
OL,19,Festablish their own probe.
